nodes.text: The EE-730 was a transport manufactured by Kuat Drive Yards that could hold 6 passengers and crew total. It could be equipped with 6 beds. The Rebel Alliance had at least one EE-730, which the Alliance used in a mission around the time of the Battle of Yavin. The transport was ambushed on Taanab and Caluan Ematt was captured.
